# Code-review gate (SOC2 CC8 change management). A PR touching a covered path
# requires review from the in-scope maintainers team before it can merge (enforced
# by branch protection + require_code_owner_reviews — see .github/branch-protection.sh).
#
# IMPORTANT: create the team and add ONLY the in-scope engineers. That membership
# IS the access-wall control (SOC2 CC6) that keeps the rest of Kelsus out:
#   gh api -X PUT orgs/Kelsus/teams/refarch-maintainers/repos/Kelsus/kelsus-oss-ai-ref-arch \
#     -f permission=maintain
# Prefer individuals? Replace the team handle with @usernames.

*                       @Kelsus/refarch-maintainers

# Security-sensitive areas, called out so changes here always need maintainer review.
/infra/                 @Kelsus/refarch-maintainers
/.github/               @Kelsus/refarch-maintainers
/apps/gateway/          @Kelsus/refarch-maintainers
